.templatetablecreate
    DashboardController(v-bind:savedbtn='true',v-bind:discardbtn='true',v-bind:links='btnlinks',v-bind:heading='head' )
    Templatetablecreatecompo
        table.o_group.o_inner_group(slot='template')
            tbody
                tr
                    td.o_td_label(colspan='1')
                        label.o_form_label(for='o_field_input_154')
                            | Template Name
                    td(colspan='1', style='width: 100%;')
                        input#o_field_input_154.o_form_input.o_form_field.o_form_required(type='text' v-model='templatename')
                tr
                    td.o_td_label(colspan='1')
                        label.o_form_label(for='o_field_input_155')
                            | Active
                    td(colspan='1', style='width: 100%;')
                        .o_checkbox.o_form_field_boolean.o_form_field
                            input#o_field_input_155(type='checkbox', name='active' v-model='templateactive')
                            span
                tr
                    td.o_td_label(colspan='1')
                        label.o_form_label(for='o_field_input_156')
                            | Model
                    td(colspan='1', style='width: 100%;')
                        .o_form_field_many2one.o_form_field.o_form_required
                            .o_form_input_dropdown
                                input#o_field_input_156.o_form_input.ui-autocomplete-input(type='text', autocomplete='off' v-model='templatemodel')
                                span.o_dropdown_button(draggable='false')
                            button.fa.fa-external-link.btn.btn-default.o_external_button(draggable='false', tabindex='-1', type='button', style='display: none;')
                tr
                    td.o_td_label(colspan='1')
                        label.o_form_label(for='o_field_input_157')
                            | Filter
                    td(colspan='1', style='width: 100%;')
                        div
                            .o_form_field_many2one.o_form_field
                                .o_form_input_dropdown
                                    select(v-model='template_filter')
                                        option(v-for='option in options2', v-bind:value="option.id")
                                            | {{ option.name }}
                                button.fa.fa-external-link.btn.btn-default.o_external_button(draggable='false', tabindex='-1', type='button', style='display: none;')
                            p.oe_grey
                                b To create a new filter:
                                br
                                |                                 - Go to the Odoo document you want to filter. For instance, go to Opportunities and search on Sales Department.
                                br
                                |                                 - In this "Search" view, select the option "Save Current Filter", enter the name (Ex: Sales Department)
                                br
                                |                                 - If you select "Share with all users", link of google document in "More" options will appear for all users in opportunities of Sales Department.
                                br
                                |                                 - If you don't select "Share with all users", link of google document in "More" options will not appear for other users in opportunities of Sales Department.
                                br
                                |                                 - If filter is not specified, link of google document will appear in "More" option for all users for all opportunities.
                tr
                    td.o_td_label(colspan='1')
                        label.o_form_label(for='o_field_input_158')
                            | Template URL
                    td(colspan='1', style='width: 100%;')
                        input#o_field_input_158.o_form_input.o_form_field.o_form_required(placeholder='https://docs.google.com/document/d/abc/edit', v-model='templateurl', type='text')
                tr
                    td.o_td_label(colspan='1')
                        label.o_form_label.o_form_invisible.o_form_label_empty.o_form_label_false(for='o_field_input_159')
                            | Resource Id
                    td(colspan='1', style='width: 100%;')
                        span.o_form_field.o_form_invisible.o_form_field_empty
                tr
                    td.o_td_label(colspan='1')
                        label.o_form_label.o_form_label_help(for='o_field_input_160', data-original-title='', title='')
                            | Google Drive Name Pattern
                    td(colspan='1', style='width: 100%;')
                        div
                            input#o_field_input_160.o_form_input.o_form_field.o_form_required(type='text' v-model='templategdrivename')
                            p.oe_grey
                                | The name of the attached document can use fixed or variable data. To distinguish between documents in
                                | Google Drive, use fixed words and fields. For instance, in the example above, if you wrote Agrolait_%(name)s_Sales
                                | in the Google Drive name field, the document in your Google Drive and in Odoo attachment will be named
                                | 'Agrolait_SO0001_Sales'.